	<text_base_description>Located in a peaceful building on a quiet block this is the perfect shelter-in-place hideout. Featuring a home office, Cat6 wiring, and a commercial grade hardwired mesh Wi-Fi network - you'll have the same connectivity you'd have at the office. Take a break from work on your own private deck overlooking a tranquil, verdant garden and a lush ivy-covered wall. Located just blocks from Alta Plaza, the Presidio, and San Francisco Bay, escaping to the outdoors is easy. Top restaurants, bars, and boutiques are just a stone's throw away. In case you'd prefer to cook at home, this kitchen features a Subzero fridge, Wolf range, Monogram wine fridge, and ample storage and counter space. Enjoy your meal in the charming formal dining room. The rest of the home features modern, luxurious finishes while retaining the classic San Francisco charm - built-in cabinetry, leaded glass cabinet doors, large bay windows, box-beam ceilings, hardwood floors, and wainscoting.  </text_base_description>
